{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"One thing I wanted to say about film making is -- about this film --"},{"time":3000,"text":"in thinking about some of the wonderful talks we've heard here,"},{"time":7000,"text":"Michael Moschen, and some of the talks about music,"},{"time":9000,"text":"this idea that there is a narrative line,"},{"time":12000,"text":"and that music exists in time."},{"time":15000,"text":"A film also exists in time; it's an experience"},{"time":18000,"text":"that you should go through emotionally."},{"time":21000,"text":"And in making this film I felt that so many of the documentaries I've seen"},{"time":23000,"text":"were all about learning something,"},{"time":26000,"text":"or knowledge, or driven by talking heads, and driven by ideas."},{"time":30000,"text":"And I wanted this film to be driven by emotions,"},{"time":33000,"text":"and really to follow my journey."},{"time":35000,"text":"So instead of doing the talking head thing, instead it's composed of scenes,"},{"time":38000,"text":"and we meet people along the way."},{"time":40000,"text":"We only meet them once."},{"time":42000,"text":"They don't come back several times, so it really chronicles a journey."},{"time":45000,"text":"It's something like life, that once you get in it"},{"time":48000,"text":"you can't get out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50000,"text":"There are two clips I want to show you,"},{"time":52000,"text":"the first one is a kind of hodgepodge,"},{"time":55000,"text":"its just three little moments, four little moments"},{"time":58000,"text":"with three of the people who are here tonight."},{"time":60000,"text":"It's not the way they occur in the film,"},{"time":62000,"text":"because they are part of much larger scenes."},{"time":64000,"text":"They play off each other in a wonderful way."},{"time":67000,"text":"And that ends with a little clip of my father, of Lou,"},{"time":69000,"text":"talking about something that is very dear to him,"},{"time":71000,"text":"which is the accidents of life."},{"time":73000,"text":"I think he felt that the greatest things in life were accidental,"},{"time":76000,"text":"and perhaps not planned at all."},{"time":79000,"text":"And those three clips will be followed by a scene of"},{"time":83000,"text":"perhaps what, to me, is really his greatest building"},{"time":85000,"text":"which is a building in Dhaka, Bangladesh."},{"time":87000,"text":"He built the capital over there."},{"time":90000,"text":"And I think you'll enjoy this building, it's never been seen --"},{"time":92000,"text":"it's been still photographed, but never photographed by a film crew."},{"time":97000,"text":"We were the first film crew in there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100000,"text":"So you'll see images of this remarkable building."},{"time":103000,"text":"A couple of things to keep in mind when you see it,"},{"time":105000,"text":"it was built entirely by hand,"},{"time":107000,"text":"I think they got a crane the last year."},{"time":111000,"text":"It was built entirely by hand off bamboo scaffolding,"},{"time":114000,"text":"people carrying these baskets of concrete on their heads,"},{"time":116000,"text":"dumping them in the forms."},{"time":118000,"text":"It is the capital of the country,"},{"time":120000,"text":"and it took 23 years to build,"},{"time":123000,"text":"which is something they seem to be very proud of over there."},{"time":126000,"text":"It took as long as the Taj Mahal."},{"time":128000,"text":"Unfortunately it took so long that Lou never saw it finished."},{"time":131000,"text":"He died in 1974."},{"time":134000,"text":"The building was finished in 1983."},{"time":137000,"text":"So it continued on for many years"},{"time":139000,"text":"after he died."},{"time":142000,"text":"Think about that when you see that building,"},{"time":144000,"text":"that sometimes the things we strive for so hard in life we never get to see finished."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148000,"text":"And that really struck me about my father,"},{"time":152000,"text":"in the sense that he had such belief"},{"time":154000,"text":"that somehow, doing these things"},{"time":156000,"text":"giving in the way that he gave, that something good would come out of it,"},{"time":159000,"text":"even in the middle of a war, there was a war with Pakistan at one point,"},{"time":161000,"text":"and the construction stopped totally and he kept working,"},{"time":164000,"text":"because he felt, \"Well when the war is done"},{"time":166000,"text":"they'll need this building.\""},{"time":169000,"text":"So, those are the two clips I'm going to show."},{"time":171000,"text":"Roll that tape."},{"time":174000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":182000,"text":"Richard Saul Wurman: I remember hearing him talk at Penn."},{"time":185000,"text":"And I came home and I said to my father and mother,"},{"time":188000,"text":"\"I just met this man: doesn't have much work,"},{"time":191000,"text":"and he's sort of ugly, funny voice,"},{"time":195000,"text":"and he's a teacher at school."},{"time":197000,"text":"I know you've never heard of him, but just mark this day"},{"time":200000,"text":"that someday you will hear of him,"},{"time":203000,"text":"because he's really an amazing man.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":206000,"text":"Frank Gehry: I heard he had some kind of a fling with Ingrid Bergman. Is that true?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":212000,"text":"Nathaniel Kahn: If he did he was a very lucky man."}]},{"cues":[{"time":214000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":216000,"text":"NK: Did you hear that, really?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":217000,"text":"FG: Yeah, when he was in Rome."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220000,"text":"Moshe Safdie: He was a real nomad."},{"time":223000,"text":"And you know, when I knew him when I was in the office,"},{"time":225000,"text":"he would come in from a trip, and he would be in the office"},{"time":227000,"text":"for two or three days intensely, and he would pack up and go."},{"time":230000,"text":"You know he'd be in the office till three in the morning working with us"},{"time":234000,"text":"and there was this kind of sense of the nomad in him."},{"time":236000,"text":"I mean as tragic as his death was in a railway station,"},{"time":242000,"text":"it was so consistent with his life, you know?"},{"time":244000,"text":"I mean I often think I'm going to die in a plane,"},{"time":246000,"text":"or I'm going to die in an airport,"},{"time":248000,"text":"or die jogging without an identification on me."},{"time":251000,"text":"I don't know why I sort of carry that"},{"time":253000,"text":"from that memory of the way he died."},{"time":256000,"text":"But he was a sort of a nomad at heart."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261000,"text":"Louis Kahn: How accidental our existences are really"},{"time":264000,"text":"and how full of influence by circumstance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344000,"text":"Man: We are the morning workers who come, all the time, here"},{"time":349000,"text":"and enjoy the walking, city's beauty and the atmosphere"},{"time":353000,"text":"and this is the nicest place of Bangladesh."},{"time":357000,"text":"We are proud of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359000,"text":"NK: You're proud of it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":361000,"text":"Man: Yes, it is the national image of Bangladesh."}]},{"cues":[{"time":364000,"text":"NK: Do you know anything about the architect?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":367000,"text":"Man: Architect? I've heard about him; he's a top-ranking architect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374000,"text":"NK: Well actually I'm here because I'm the architect's son,"},{"time":377000,"text":"he was my father."}]},{"cues":[{"time":379000,"text":"Man: Oh! Dad is Louis Farrakhan?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":381000,"text":"NK: Yeah. No not Louis Farrakhan, Louis Kahn."}]},{"cues":[{"time":384000,"text":"Man: Louis Kahn, yes!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":387000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":389000,"text":"Man: Your father, is he alive?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":391000,"text":"NK: No, he's been dead for 25 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394000,"text":"Man: Very pleased to welcome you back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":397000,"text":"NK: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438000,"text":"NK: He never saw it finished, Pop."},{"time":440000,"text":"No, he never saw this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465000,"text":"Shamsul Wares: It was almost impossible, building for a country like ours."},{"time":469000,"text":"In 30, 50 years back, it was nothing, only paddy fields,"},{"time":473000,"text":"and since we invited him here,"},{"time":476000,"text":"he felt that he has got a responsibility."},{"time":478000,"text":"He wanted to be a Moses here, he gave us democracy."},{"time":481000,"text":"He is not a political man,"},{"time":483000,"text":"but in this guise he has given us"},{"time":485000,"text":"the institution for democracy, from where we can rise."},{"time":488000,"text":"In that way it is so relevant."},{"time":492000,"text":"He didn't care for how much money this country has,"},{"time":494000,"text":"or whether he would be able to ever finish this building,"},{"time":497000,"text":"but somehow he has been able to do it, build it, here."},{"time":500000,"text":"And this is the largest project he has got in here, the poorest country in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":505000,"text":"NK: It cost him his life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":507000,"text":"SW: Yeah, he paid. He paid his life for this,"},{"time":510000,"text":"and that is why he is great and we'll remember him."},{"time":514000,"text":"But he was also human."},{"time":516000,"text":"Now his failure to satisfy the family life,"},{"time":521000,"text":"is an inevitable association of great people."},{"time":524000,"text":"But I think his son will understand this,"},{"time":527000,"text":"and will have no sense of grudge,"},{"time":529000,"text":"or sense of being neglected, I think."},{"time":532000,"text":"He cared in a very different manner,"},{"time":535000,"text":"but it takes a lot of time to understand that."},{"time":537000,"text":"In social aspect of his life"},{"time":541000,"text":"he was just like a child, he was not at all matured."},{"time":543000,"text":"He could not say no to anything,"},{"time":545000,"text":"and that is why, that he cannot say no to things,"},{"time":548000,"text":"we got this building today."},{"time":551000,"text":"You see, only that way you can be able to understand him."},{"time":554000,"text":"There is no other shortcut,"},{"time":557000,"text":"no other way to really understand him."},{"time":560000,"text":"But I think he has given us this building"},{"time":568000,"text":"and we feel all the time for him,"},{"time":570000,"text":"that's why, he has given love for us."},{"time":573000,"text":"He could not probably give the right kind of love for you,"},{"time":576000,"text":"but for us, he has given the people the right kind of love,"},{"time":579000,"text":"that is important."},{"time":581000,"text":"You have to understand that."},{"time":583000,"text":"He had an enormous amount of love,"},{"time":585000,"text":"he loved everybody."},{"time":587000,"text":"To love everybody, he sometimes did not see"},{"time":591000,"text":"the very closest ones,"},{"time":594000,"text":"and that is inevitable for men of his stature."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}